# Crawler Architecture

Keep the crawler modular.

Preferred package layout:

```text
src/skill_scanning_crawler/
├── discovery/
├── github_client/
├── metadata/
├── validation/
├── deduplication/
├── download/
├── export/
├── reports/
└── common/
```

Do not implement the crawler as one giant script.

Each pipeline stage must have a clear input and output.

Pipeline stages:

1. curated seed ingestion,
2. GitHub search discovery,
3. repository identity normalization,
4. repository metadata enrichment,
5. tree scanning,
6. skill location,
7. validation,
8. deduplication,
9. ranking,
10. snapshot download,
11. manifest export,
12. summary reporting.

Prefer typed data models over loose dictionaries at module boundaries.
